highlights.text: Hov1 has the most spots on Top Songs Sweden. “Hon dansar vidare i livet” is the highest at #20.
“Babblarnas vaggvisa” by Babblarna has been on Top Songs Sweden the longest, at 1688 days straight.

“Vill du ha mig?” by Thomas Stenström is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Sweden, up 140 spots at #27.
